The paper proposes a novel adversarial domain adaptation method using deep learning techniques. The method is evaluated on image datasets and text datasets, indicating that it could belong to several sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
